    {
        "content": "<p>When you see</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"k\">let</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">val</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">←</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">←</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">mvarId</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">getType</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">←</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">mvarId</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">getTag</span><span class=\"o\">)</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>you should interpret this to mean</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"k\">let</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">tmp1</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">←</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">mvarId</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">getType</span>\n<span class=\"k\">let</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">tmp2</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">←</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">mvarId</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">getTag</span>\n<span class=\"k\">let</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">val</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">←</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">tmp1</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">tmp2</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>The arrow notation is \"lifted out\".</p>",
        "id": 528545683,
        "sender_full_name": "Kyle Miller",
        "timestamp": 1752429052
    }
